# =========================
# API Keys / Secret Configs
# (store these INSIDE .env, never directly in code)
# Examples:
# SENDGRID_API_KEY
# JWT_SECRET
# MONGO_URI
# CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET
# RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET
# SMTP_PASSWORD
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
# FIREBASE_ADMIN_KEY
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET
# =========================

